     FASNPW00 CF  E                    WORKSTN
     F                                        RRN1  KSFILE SFL01
     F                                        RRN3  KSFILE SFL03
     FAB#PL76 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAB#PL75 UF  E           K        DISK
     F            AB#PP751                          KRENAMEAB#PL75R
     FAB#PL78 UF  E           K        DISK
